我们喜欢叫自己“城市黑客”!当都市人一边叫嚣拥挤,一边浪费大量闲置空间,建筑师出身的我们于是我们创立了“好处MeetBest”这个城市空间品牌,穿梭在城市罅隙,探寻城市中的有趣空间,挖掘空间中的城市故事｡我们希望借由“好处MeetBest”,能够不断激发城市人对生活的无限想象力,为大家发现美好聚处,更希望能够得到你的喜欢｡

We are a group of architects in Shanghai and our brand is 好处 MeetBest. We have studied and lived in US, Japan, Taiwan, Hong Kong, and we all believe in urban hacker style. We find out interesting spaces scattered inside the city and turn them into social spaces available to everyone. Enjoy our spaces and you will discover the beauty of the city you have ever seen!
